<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +3</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1 (200 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Pounce.</em></strong> If the deinonychus moves at least 20 feet straight toward a creature and then hits it with a claw attack on the same turn, that target must succeed on a DC 12 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. If the target is prone, the deinonychus can make one bite attack against it as a bonus action.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The deinonychus makes three attacks: one with its bite and two with its claws.</p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 6 (1d8+2) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Claw.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 6 (1d8+2) slashing damage.</p>

